Hi,

I've just applied the patch 2. It solves all the problems I encountered.
Indeed, I'm able to compil files that use labeled function arguments.
Moreover, with NT Emacs I succeed in using the "show type at point" feature.

(I use the mingw version compiled with Win XP + cygwin)

